<paragraph id="8B90A945FFBAFFEEDAD6F8E0FE60FDB9" blockId="6.[128,768,398,550]" pageId="6" pageNumber="15">
Ty p e. Designated here. 
<taxonomicName id="4C2FD2C6FFBAFFEEDBACF8E0FE5CFE59" authority="STERNBERG, 1820, p. 23" authorityName="STERNBERG" authorityPageNumber="23" authorityYear="1820" class="Lycopodiopsida" family="Lepidodendraceae" genus="Lepidodendron" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lepidodendrales" pageId="6" pageNumber="15" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aculeatum">
<emphasis id="B95B7557FFBAFFEEDBACF8E0FD2AFE39" box="[476,767,398,422]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="15">Lepidodendron aculeatum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFBED4B4FFBAFFEEDAF1F8C0FEE8FE59" author="Sternberg, K. M. von" box="[129,317,430,454]" pageId="6" pageNumber="15" refId="ref20641" refString="Sternberg, K. M. von (1820): Versuch einer geognostischbotanischen Darstellung der Flora der Vorwelt, Vol. I. 1. - in Commission im Deutschen Museum, F. Fleischer, Leipzig, 24 pp." type="book" year="1820">STERNBERG, 1820</bibRefCitation>
